      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施工作节点的状态流转图。这个节点从启动后先进入Idle状态，收到Start Request后变成Loading，然后可能成功也可能失败。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Start Request"
