      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那Loading之后的两个分支我理解是：数据正常收到就走到Success，请求失败就走到Error，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Data Received",
        "Request Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。而且Success之后可以Reset回到Idle，Error之后也有两条路：Retry回Idle，或者Abort直接回到工作节点本身。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Idle",
        "Reset",
        "Error",
        "Retry",
        "Abort",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我用stateDiagram-v2来画，把Infra_WorkerNode作为起始节点，Idle、Loading、Success、Error四个状态，以及它们之间的转移关系都标上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Abort那条线是指工作节点直接退出当前任务流吗？我需要确认一下箭头终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Abort",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Abort是从Error状态直接指回Infra_WorkerNode，表示放弃当前状态机回到节点层面。其他转移：Loading到Success是Data Received，Loading到Error是Request Failed，都没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Abort",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Data Received",
        "Request Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没问题。不过Reset和Retry的触发条件要区分清楚，Reset是正常完成后的重置，Retry是失败后的重试。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reset",
        "Success",
